  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Your Claymore is unbreakable and you cannot be disarmed of it against your will.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">You can use Dexterity as your Taijutsu ability modifier for your Claymore Clan Hijutsu for all calculations.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">If a creature other than you would attempt to wield this weapon it gains the Two-Handed property.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Starting at 11th level your mastery over your weapon far exceeds your previous level and you can now utilize your weapon more efficiently. Your Claymore now does 2d8 slashing damage and once per turn when you damage a creature or a creature fails a saving throw with this weapon you can force them to make a Constitution saving throw against your Taijutsu Save DC or gain 1 rank of weakened.</span></p>",
